Sentencas: The accuracy and reliability of solid oxide fuel cell (SOFC) modeling mainly depend on the precise extraction and optimization of some unknown parameters.
Titulo: Grasshopper Optimization Algorithms for Parameter Extraction of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: However, the SOFC model is a multi-peak, nonlinear, multivariable, and strongly combined system.
Titulo: Grasshopper Optimization Algorithms for Parameter Extraction of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: In the previous decisive optimization methods, it is difficult to achieve satisfactory parameter extraction.
Titulo: Grasshopper Optimization Algorithms for Parameter Extraction of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Therefore, this article proposes a SOFC parameter extraction method based on the superhuman algorithm and extracts several important parameters of the SOFC model.
Titulo: Grasshopper Optimization Algorithms for Parameter Extraction of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: In addition, the electrochemical model (ECM), which is a typical SOFC model, has also been studied to verify the extraction performance of the glass jump optimization algorithm (GOA) under various working conditions.
Titulo: Grasshopper Optimization Algorithms for Parameter Extraction of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells

Sentencas: Simulation results based on MATLAB show that GOA can greatly improve the accuracy, speed, and stability of inferring these unknown parameters through a comprehensive comparison with the particle swarm optimization (PSO) algorithm.
Titulo: Grasshopper Optimization Algorithms for Parameter Extraction of Solid Oxide Fuel Cells
